               Death
            </rs>.)</p>
               <p>(Bailey and Cheetham were <rs id="t17801206-46-verdict237" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17801206-46-verdict237" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801206-46-verdict237" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               humbly recommended by the Jury to his Majesty's mercy
